"use strict";(self.webpackChunknz_life_handbook=self.webpackChunknz_life_handbook||[]).push([[517],{4710:(a,e,n)=>{n.r(e),n.d(e,{comp:()=>i,data:()=>r});var s=n(641);const t={},i=(0,n(6262).A)(t,[["render",function(a,e){return(0,s.uX)(),(0,s.CE)("div",null,e[0]||(e[0]=[(0,s.Fv)('<h1 id="compx519-malware-analysis-and-penetration-testing" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#compx519-malware-analysis-and-penetration-testing"><span>COMPX519-Malware Analysis and Penetration Testing</span></a></h1><p><a href="https://www.waikato.ac.nz/study/papers/compx519/2025/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">COMPX519 Malware Analysis and Penetration Testing 官方课程链接（如有）</a></p><h2 id="推荐指数" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#推荐指数"><span>推荐指数</span></a></h2><p>对安全方向有兴趣的同学可以考虑下</p><h2 id="课程简介" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#课程简介"><span>课程简介</span></a></h2><p><strong>COMPX519-24B (HAM) - Malware Analysis and Penetration Testing</strong><br> 恶意软件分析和渗透测试<br> 注意，这是一个二合一的课程，学了之后发现其实是一个三合一的课程。</p><p>这个课程好像在不断变化，但是只要是同一个个老师课，核心内容和模块不会变。</p><p>主要分为三个模块：</p><ul><li>恶意软件分析，主要针对 Windows 平台</li><li>汇编语言</li><li>渗透测试，主要针对 SQL 注入攻击和 XSS</li></ul><h2 id="是否需要签到" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#是否需要签到"><span>是否需要签到？</span></a></h2><p>不</p><h2 id="内容难度" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#内容难度"><span>内容难度</span></a></h2><p>没有计算机原理基础的会学这课比较困难，涉及一些操作系统和汇编的内容。</p><h2 id="考试形式" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#考试形式"><span>考试形式</span></a></h2><p>100 分考试内容，闭卷考试，包括选择题，简答题，场景题。</p><h2 id="考核难度" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#考核难度"><span>考核难度</span></a></h2><p>一共三次作业，都是实操为主。<br> 需要注意的是作业对电脑硬件要求很高，但是学校提供了机房，不用自己折腾。<br> 老师已经准备好了虚拟机镜像文件，不用自己折腾环境。<br> 老师还准备好了移动硬盘，不用自己买。<br> 最重要的是看作业要求，不要把病毒放出来！</p><h2 id="是否容易拿高分" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#是否容易拿高分"><span>是否容易拿高分？</span></a></h2><p>不太容易，最后一个闭卷考试会拉开差距。</p><h2 id="需要基础" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#需要基础"><span>需要基础</span></a></h2><p>需要计算机原理基础，特别是操作系统和汇编语言的基础知识。</p><h2 id="实用程度" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#实用程度"><span>实用程度</span></a></h2><p>对我来说最大收获是汇编语言这块，加深了我对编程基础知识的理解。其次是加强了安全意识。</p>',23)]))}]]),r=JSON.parse('{"path":"/courses/compx519.html","title":"COMPX519-Malware Analysis and Penetration Testing","lang":"zh-CN","frontmatter":{},"git":{"updatedTime":1752877642000,"contributors":[{"name":"Xiaodong Yan","username":"","email":"xy191@students.waikato.ac.nz","commits":5}],"changelog":[{"hash":"4cfe2aa44a4771c1a4dfa8c975f0b90458459553","time":1752877642000,"email":"xy191@students.waikato.ac.nz","author":"Xiaodong Yan","message":"Remove outdated files and transition project from Docsify to VuePress 2.0, enhancing documentation structure and user experience. Update README with new project features and links, and delete unnecessary scripts and markdown files."},{"hash":"740dc8b97cca2ef47eed32f8319be1a2177e1446","time":1752659990000,"email":"xy191@students.waikato.ac.nz","author":"Xiaodong Yan","message":"Update"},{"hash":"e41ac8ec0fa85ca9d8e2148fb98b48a8545c2ee0","time":1751964944000,"email":"xy191@students.waikato.ac.nz","author":"Xiaodong Yan","message":"Update"},{"hash":"5556faf2479a8320ee4c47a20e0a29ed2d534ef9","time":1751876455000,"email":"xy191@students.waikato.ac.nz","author":"Xiaodong Yan","message":"Update doc"},{"hash":"66a53bcdadf53faccbc9b2b039ec9755f3a77955","time":1751875949000,"email":"xy191@students.waikato.ac.nz","author":"Xiaodong Yan","message":"init: only keep latest snapshot"}]},"filePathRelative":"courses/compx519.md"}')}}]);